data.name: cbPowercam.ToolTip
data.value: This enables the ability to override camera transition reinstatements by the game. Allows to hard-freeze the camera ANYWHERE without it zooming out. May break some transitions while enabled. Use with caution.

data.name: chbAutoApply.ToolTip
data.value:
This will automatically update the animation to be replaced with the animation selected in the second box whenever the second box changes.
Note: May glitch with some animations.
